Furthermore, the plastics industry is a major end-user of synthetic iron oxide pigments for coloring plastic products. With advancements in pigment technologies and the rising emphasis on eco-friendly alternatives, market players are focusing on sustainable practices to meet evolving customer demands. The pharmaceutical sector presents opportunities for the use of synthetic iron oxide pigments in coatings and formulations.

